## Development

### Setup for Contributors

```bash
# Clone
git clone https://github.com/abdullafajal/django-vue-start.git
cd django-vue-start

# Install
pip install -e .

# Test
pytest tests/ -v
```

## Publishing

### PyPI
```bash
pip install build twine
python -m build
twine upload dist/*
```

### npm
```bash
npm publish --otp=YOUR_2FA_CODE
```

